title: Was the goddess Oshun Beyonce's Grammy Award inspiration?
text: show ad Revealed: African goddess of water and fertility that blesses mothers with TWINS who Beyonc√© paid homage to at last night's Grammy's (and in Lemonade) The star looked to be channeling Oshun - a Yoruba deity from West Africa for whom twins and motherhood are particularly crucial Also called Osun, her wrath and power was respected by male deities in creation Harvard divinity professor Dr Jacob Olupona said of Beyonce: 'She is speaking to the world, she is speaking to America'
